93		// Default-path contract (ddx-755f5881 AC #1): an empty dispatch input
94		// (no rawArgs, no workers.default_spec) must produce a spec with
95		// Profile: "default" and nothing else. This eliminates the historical
96		// 19-burn drain-queue failure mode where an empty spec fanned out into
97		// per-tier ladder iteration with no upstream synthesis target.
